  <div class="feature-text">
    <h2>Customise every detail</h2>
    <p>Change the look of your text, add a drop shadow to an image, fill shapes with colour and more — you can modify everything in your document. You can even wrap text around images, link text boxes so the text flows from one box to the next, or use mail merge to automatically personalise multiple documents.</p>
    <a href="/docs/article-one/" class="feature-link">Intro to customisation <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></a>
