  <div class="feature-text">
    <h2>Become a publisher</h2>
    <p>DZDocs comes with book templates that let you create interactive books in EPUB format. Add text and images — and even a table of contents. When you're ready, you can make your book available for purchase or download in Apple Books.</p>
